    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but my doctor is so old school and just keeps saying the same thing over and over. i feel like i'm being held back by these chemicals. i saw a video about how a high dose of garlic extract is basically a natural anticoagulant and if i combine that with a really heavy intake of vitamin K, it should balance everything out naturally. wouldn't that be more stable than the warfarin which jumps around so much? wouldn't that be a safer way to do it?",
